Two fonts, driven by CSS custom properties in `src/styles/variables/typography.css`:

| Role | Font | CSS Variable |
|---|---|---|
| **Headings** (H1–H4) | Space Grotesk Variable | `--lvr-font-family-heading` |
| **Body** (P, Lead, Small, lists) | Recursive Variable (sans) | `--lvr-font-family-body` |
| **Code** (InlineCode) | Recursive Variable (mono) | `--lvr-font-family-code` |
| **UI chrome** (available but not yet used) | Recursive Variable (sans) | `--lvr-font-family-ui` |

Both are variable fonts loaded via `@fontsource-variable` in `index.css`:

```css
@import "@fontsource-variable/space-grotesk";
@import "@fontsource-variable/recursive/full.css";
```

One note — `dev-layout.module.css` hardcodes `font-family: ui-monospace, monospace` instead of using the token. The Badge component uses `--lvr-font-family-mono`. Both are Recursive under the hood, just via different paths.

